* if current number nums[i] is 3 mod 1 then update the dp[1] value with min between num[i] and dp[1]
* Also we update the dp[2] value cause 2 dp[1] value can make 1 dp[2] value EX => 1 + 1 = 2.
* if current number nums[i] is 3 mod 2 then update the dp[2] value with min between num[i] and dp[2]
